			<div class="body">

                <b>Can I take your food tour if I have dietary restrictions or allergies?</b><br/>
                If you have any food allergies, dietary restrictions, or other special requirements, we ask that you notify us before booking. While we can provide some option for vegetarians, guests should be aware that often, tastings such as kebab meats cannot be replaced with a vegetarian alternative as the stores we visit specialize in those dishes.
                <br/><br/>
                <b>Can I get a discount if I am not eating on the tour or eat less on the tour?</b><br/>
                As we have limited space on our tours, we cannot offer discounts based on the quantity of food consumed. The price is all-inclusive of tastings, guided tour and return ferry tickets.
                <br/><br/>
                <b>How much food is served on your food tour?</b><br/>
                The tour includes a full meal's worth of tastings. We encourage you not to have a big breakfast before the tour begins.

